// `@file("path")` reads a project-rooted file at comptime ; when the
// target doesn't exist, TS emits C4006. Vader's codes.vader maps C4006
// to a generic TypeMismatch, so this snippet exposes which code Vader
// chose to use for the ENOENT path (if any).
module "snippet"

@comptime
export DATA :: @file("definitely_not_a_real_file.txt")

main :: fn() -> i32 {
    return 0
}
